title: Trump Pushes Executive Orders: A Closer Look | Ellen Waggett & Jo Winiarski: Late Night Chats
description:
Seth takes a closer look at Donald Trump's new plan to cut taxes on corporations.
Then, in a new Late Night Chats segment, Ellen Waggett and Jo Winiarski of the Late Night art department discuss their work.
